Any AI training done on this Work without the Owner's explicit consent is considered a severe violation. If discovered, the offending party shall owe the Owner liquidated damages of **ONE MILLION UNITED STATES DOLLARS (USD $1,000,000)** per token processed or used in any training run, dataset, or model. 

This penalty reflects the Owner's view that unauthorized extraction and exploitation of their labor by AI systems is equivalent to digital theft on an industrial scale. The Owner reserves the right to pursue additional punitive damages, injunctive relief, and all other remedies available under law.

